18/12/2008
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- Mafia boss Ismet Bajramovic-Celo, former commander of the military police, was found dead on Wednesday (December 17th) in his apartment in the Ciglana district of the capital.
The circumstances surrounding his death are unclear, but police believe he died from a drug overdose.
(Dnevni Avaz, Netpress, NTV Hayat, Glas Sprske - 17/12/08)
